          <p>First, measure the distance around your waist in inches. Second, using the handy"Waist Measurement"chart, follow it to the measurement you got from your waist, then draw an imaginary line, in your head, straight down to the "Black Anchor Belt Sizes" chart.</p>
          <p>Wherever your straight imaginary line lands is the size of belt that would fit you!</p>
