          <h2>Shipping Policy</h2>
          <h3>Domestic</h3>
          <p>Tracking numbers are provided for all orders shipped to the USA. Confirmation emails will be sent upon delivery. We ship via USPS, so please allow 24 hours for the tracking number to populate within the USPS tracking system.</p>
          <h3>International</h3>
          <p>All International orders are shipped via USPS. Tracking numbers are not included for international orders. Customs fees incurred from importing goods are not Black Anchors responsibility.</p>
          <h3>All Orders</h3>
          <p>Rejected packages and all additional costs related to shipping are assumed by the customer. <b>Please allow 7 to 14 days for orders to ship after they are placed because of the made to order nature of our business.</b></p>
          <h2>Return &amp; Exchange Policy</h2>
          <p>If you receive your order and it’s not what you expected, we apologize, but we do not accept returns or exchanges. When ordering from Black Anchor you are ordering from a very small team of crafts people who put heart, soul, and skill into each and every product. We craft each piece with close attention to detail, and we do not make it until it is ordered.</p>
          <p>Because of this made-to-order methodology we do not accept returns or exchanges. Please head over to <b>"Lifetime Guarantee"</b> to find out about our guarantee on your purchase.</p>
